{"tid":1282874,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"發夢戴住Anonymous面具會唔會有一石二鳥之效？","createTime":"2019-07-03T16:17:35.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-05T00:01:19.000Z","uid":32544,"like":42,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"21987111fccb90579205b0040fd37ceb7f65a3c4","tid":1282874,"uid":32544,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T16:17:35.000Z","msg":"Anonymous早期示威者會將面具以及統一服飾著出街<br />\n<br />\n啱啱發夢見到有一大班人都戴住Anonymous面具出街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n咁會唔會號召到真Anonymous注意，又符合Anonymous理念。<br />\n<br />\n最重要嘅係令到夢入面嘅芝娃娃唔可以亂咁咬人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6149cbe2994c4c6c076029df8435895be2a7b33f","tid":1282874,"uid":32544,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T16:18:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>其實佢地有過咩重要戰役</blockquote>起哂成班3k 黨出黎</blockquote>KKK <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n極端到</blockquote><br />\n\t<br />\n\t<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=2FclnNWrwkA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D2FclnNWrwkA&d=3FtZuWe%2BwKi7N9uEGSTnHjDyw%2Fr9SRfH8QBX8OZV2FM%3D&h=d060ed1a\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=2FclnNWrwkA</a><br />\n\t<br />\n<br />\n\t<br />\n\t<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=R8BefS3iuFc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DR8BefS3iuFc&d=3FtZuWe%2BwKi7N9uEGSTnHjDyw%2Fr9SRfH8QBX8OZV2FM%3D&h=8d6a9b8f\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=R8BefS3iuFc</a><br />\n\t<br />\n<br />\n\t<br />\n\t<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=dByYZ6DBmGM\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DdByYZ6DBmGM&d=3FtZuWe%2BwKi7N9uEGSTnHjDyw%2Fr9SRfH8QBX8OZV2FM%3D&h=11f343de\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=dByYZ6DBmGM</a><br />\n\t<br />\n<br />\n\t<br />\n\